data.description: BRAND NEW AC UNIT w/ 10 year parts and 2 year labor warranty. This little gem is a must see! Very well cared for 3 bed/2 bath townhome located in a quiet gated community. Gorgeous Granite in newly remodeled kitchen. 18'' tile with carpet in the 3 bedrooms. The home has a nice separate layout, great for shared living or guests. Living room has built-in and gas fireplace. Guest bath remodeled w/walk-in shower. Granite in bathrooms. Front yard is HOA maintained/back is on timer. Nice 2 car garage with painted floor. This area has nearby restaurants, coffee shops, fast food, carwashes, churches, gas stations, Goodwill, Hospital, Home Depot, etc. The grocery store is about a 2 minute drive and only 5 minutes to Walmart, movie theatre, and LOTS more. Conveniently located near the US 60 and 202.
